dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Miliaria Germanica Communia".
Two bar scales on inset map (right) given in "Eydersteetsche rRoede van 16 voeten." and "Virgae Eyderstedienses 16 pedum."
Indexes: op de Eyder; op de Elve; op de Weser.
Decorative cartouches, compass roses, rhumb lines, ships.
Pictorial vignettes of figures and city views along border.
